# App restart after changes

When you make any code or asset change to this project:

1. **Close** any running instance of the app:
   - Kill process `MabaControlCenter` if present.
   - Optionally stop any `dotnet` process that is hosting this app (e.g. by matching window title or by being the one that was launched from this project).

2. **Open** the app again:
   - From the project root: `dotnet run` (run in background so the window can be used).

Do this yourself as part of the same change; do not ask the user to restart manually.
